description:
### Context

This dataset includes all detectable faces of the sample training dataset in [Deepfake Detection Challenge](https://www.kaggle.com/c/deepfake-detection-challenge/). Kaggle and the host expected and encouraged us to train our models outside of Kaggle’s notebooks environment; however, for someone who prefers to stick to Kaggle's kernels, this dataset would help a lot 😄.
